description: Bring your funky vibe to the progressive, artsy community of Gulfport. This  charming two bedroom, two bath, one car garage colorful charmer is  located just a quick walk to the waterfront marina dotted with bobbing  sailboats and floating pelicans as well as the historic downtown area on  Boca Ciega Bay. Pull in to your circular drive way surrounded by an easy to  maintain xeriscaped yard. Upon entering your art deco home, you will feel  hugged by warmth and peacefulness. From the entry foyer, head to the  dining area with a wall of windows welcoming in the Florida sunshine. A  modern, classy kitchen is designed with marbled granite counters, built in  wine rack, wine fridge and a convenient pass through window. The  bathrooms are immaculate, keeping the vintage feel alive while the  bedrooms are cozy. Vacation in your own backyard paradise on the  covered patio engulfed in tropical bamboo. Saunter along the paved paths  through colorful plants in your ample, fenced outdoor garden. Schedule  your private tour today!
